data.name: lblZPN.ToolTip
data.value: Enhances ZeroKore's performance (especially on lower-end PC's) by using native C++ libraries for logic. You will not be able to alter features using the In-Game Menu and cannot pause the deployment.

data.name: lblAA.ToolTip
data.value: Actively scans for the closest player to the player's crosshair (centre of screen) and highlights the target. When the ALT key is pressed, ZeroKore® will aim at the enemy's head. NOTE: Raw Input must be disabled for this to work.
